    "The objective is to identify the top K most likely words from V, this set of words is represented as TopK(q i) and is defined as:",
    "Lexical Simplification involves replacing a word in context with a simpler alternatives (Paetzold and Specia, 2016).",
    "To analyze the ability of our KidLM models to generate simpler words within a given context, we utilized the TSAR-EN dataset (Štajner et al., 2022), annotated by MTurk annotators who are required to be at least 18 years old.",
